<section id="html-basic">
  <h2>HTML Basic</h2>
  <p>This is a basic example of an HTML page:</p>
  <pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;My First Page&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Hello World&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;This is my first HTML page.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</code></pre>
